          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-03-17 16:16:13" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(a figurative extension of meaning of {L:σωρεύω&lt;SDBG:σωρεύω:000000&gt;} ‘to heap up’; see {D:25.199}) to be engaged intensively and extensively in some activity</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to be given over to doing</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to be fully engaged in</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is possible to interpret the usage of σωρεύομαι in {S:05500300600026} as referring to a state of being ‘burdened by sins’ or ‘burdened by the guilt of sin.’</Comments>
